<p>Bachelor Chow.  Serves 1 (duh).</p>
<p><img src="/images/bachelor_chow.jpg" alt="[now with flavor]" /></p>
<ol>
<li>Make some ramen noodles.  Feel free to substitute whatever other pasta or rice you have on hand.</li>
<li>Drain water.  Use of a collinder is discouraged, because a true bachelor will make this with one pot and one fork.  No other dishes to wash.</li>
<li>Add a can of Hormel chili with beans. Mix together.</li>
<li>Heat on medium until everything is hot.</li>
<li>Eat</li>
</ol>
<p>This meal costs less than a dollar.  You get what you pay for.</p>

